        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Overseas Americans Financial Access Act</b></p> <p>This bill modifies tax reporting requirements that apply to foreign financial institutions and individuals with foreign financial assets to create exceptions for the foreign accounts of certain U.S. residents or citizens living abroad.</p>]]>
        </text>
